name: AuthController
desc:
Controller for managing authentication state and operations.
Handles both authenticated users and guest mode with session UUID system
for database operations (RFC 4122 compliant).

name: currentUser
desc: Gets the current authenticated user

name: getUserIdForMessaging
desc:
Determines the user ID to use for database operations (message sending).
Returns a tuple of (userId, isGuest).

name: signInAnonymously
desc:
Attempts to sign in anonymously
Returns null if falling back to guest mode

name: AuthErrorWidget
desc: Widget that displays authentication error UI

name: build
desc: Describes the part of the user interface represented by this widget.

name: toString
desc: A string representation of this object.

name: getHumanReadableName
desc:
Get human-readable name from session UUID for display purposes.
Uses the session UUID (not day-based guest ID) to generate a consistent
4-word name using vocabulary mapping for the same session.

name: getSessionUserId
desc:
Get the session UUID for database operations and name generation.
Returns a RFC 4122 compliant UUID that's compatible with PostgreSQL.
